OL,3,CAbingdon Reservoir costs 'spiralling
OL,4,Cout of control', Oxfordshire MPs claim
OL,6,FThree Oxfordshire MPs have claimed
OL,7,Fthat the estimated costs of building a
OL,8,Fnew reservoir near Abingdon are
OL,9,F"spiralling out of control".
OL,11,FThe price tag for the project ` known
OL,12,Fas South East Strategic Reservoir
OL,13,FOption ` has increased from #2.2bn to
OL,14,Fup to #7.5bn.
OL,16,FLiberal Democrats Olly Glover, Layla
OL,17,FMoran and Charlie Maynard argue the
OL,18,Frising price tag "significantly
OL,19,Fundermines the business case and risks
OL,20,Fleaving bill payers liable".
