OL,3,CAbingdon Reservoir costs 'spiralling
OL,4,Cout of control', Oxfordshire MPs claim
OL,6,FIn a letter to the Environment
OL,7,FSecretary, Emma Reynolds, the group of
OL,8,FMPs call on the government to pause
OL,9,Fand review the options for securing
OL,10,Fwater supply.
OL,12,FThames Water's Leonie Dubois told ITV
OL,13,FNews Meridian that the company
OL,14,F"remains confident that the reservoir
OL,15,Fis the best value option to secure
OL,16,Fwater supplies for 15 million people".
OL,18,FShe added: "The South East faces an
OL,19,Furgent and growing threat from
OL,20,Fdrought. As one of the driest regions
OL,21,Fin the country, we must act now."
