OL,3,CAbingdon Reservoir costs 'spiralling
OL,4,Cout of control', Oxfordshire MPs claim
OL,6,FThe company is expected to apply to
OL,7,Fthe government for a development
OL,8,Fconsent order later this year. If
OL,9,Fapproved, construction could begin in
OL,10,F2028 with completion in 2043.
OL,12,FNo new major reservoirs have been
OL,13,Fbuilt in England since 1992 but the
OL,14,FLabour government has committed to
OL,15,Fopening 9 new ones before 2050.
