OL,3,CAbingdon Reservoir costs 'spiralling
OL,4,Cout of control', Oxfordshire MPs claim
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,7,Fthe Environment, Food and Rural
OL,8,FAffairs (Defra) said: "We face growing
OL,9,Fpressures on our water resources, and
OL,10,Fwith a changing climate, those
OL,11,Fpressures will only increase."
OL,13,F"The proposed South East Strategic
OL,14,FReservoir Option project is
OL,15,Fprogressing through the required
OL,16,Fplanning stages.
OL,18,F"The project is subject to
OL,19,Fconsultation and would be examined by
OL,20,Fthe Planning Inspectorate before
OL,21,Fdevelopment consent could be granted."
